Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.17,0:01:00.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,大家好\N{\fs90}Hello, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.91,0:01:03.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs90}Hello. Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.15,0:01:06.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,大家好\N{\fs90}Greetings!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.52,0:01:10.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,这儿还是这样\N{\fs90}That doesn't get any worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.26,0:01:14.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,你好\N{\fs90}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.16,0:01:18.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,欢迎大家\N{\fs90}Hello, and welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:20.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到Grand Tour\N{\fs90}Welcome to The Grand Tour,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.33,0:01:22.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,这次 我们还是在\N{\fs90}which, once again, comes to you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.43,0:01:25.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,苏格兰的尼斯湖畔\N{\fs90}from the shores of Loch Ness in Scotland.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.64,0:01:29.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的\N{\fs90}Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.41,0:01:34.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们之所以还在这儿\N{\fs90}The reason why we're still here is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.34,0:01:35.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,是因为上次节目后\N{\fs90}after last week's show,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.88,0:01:39.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,他俩和一个当地人交流了一下\N{\fs90}these two got talking to a man in the local town,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.38,0:01:41.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,他和他们说\N{\fs90}who has convinced them that,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.25,0:01:44.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,这湖里有个怪兽\N{\fs90}in that lake, there is a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.32,0:01:47.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里的确有个怪兽\N{\fs90}Well, there is a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.36,0:01:48.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,你见过吗\N{\fs90}Have you seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.89,0:01:51.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,没 但那人很有说服力\N{\fs90}No, but the man was very convincing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.39,0:01:53.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,他是不是卖给你一块\N{\fs90}Did he sell you a tea towel
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.20,0:01:55.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,印着怪兽的抹布\N{\fs90}with a drawing of the monster on it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:59.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 现在我们知道怪兽长啥样了\N{\fs90}He did, and now we know what the monster looks like.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.10,0:02:02.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,正是 我们还有怪兽的照片\N{\fs90}Exactly. We've also got photographs of the monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.44,0:02:04.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,-看这张照片 -这是块木头\N{\fs90}- Look, we've got this one. - That's a log.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.91,0:02:07.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有这张 看哪\N{\fs90}And we've got this one. Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.48,0:02:09.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,-怪兽 -还是木头\N{\fs90}- Monster. - Another log.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:12.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,你们来看看这张照片吧 就是它\N{\fs90}Can I just draw your attention to a picture I've got? Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.81,0:02:14.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,这不是怪兽吧\N{\fs90}Well, that's not a monster, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.75,0:02:17.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 那是个象鼩 好眼力\N{\fs90}No, that is an elephant shrew. Well spotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.75,0:02:21.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,这可是动物中的GT-R\N{\fs90}Now, this is the Nissan GT-R among animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.99,0:02:24.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,你见过它跑起来吗 非常惊人\N{\fs90}Have you ever seen it on the move? It's phenomenal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:27.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,它留下一条尾流 过弯时就像有下压力\N{\fs90}It leaves a rooster tail and it corners like it's got downforce.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.66,0:02:31.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的意思是 这是种非常珍稀的动物\N{\fs90}But my point is, this is a very rare animal,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:35.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且它的照片是高清全彩的\N{\fs90}and yet the photograph of it is in sharp focus and colour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.91,0:02:40.04,字幕,,0,0,0,, 你们那些怪兽照片都是黑白的\N{\fs90}Now, all the pictures of your monster are in black and white.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.11,0:02:42.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,-可能怪兽就是黑白的 -而且模糊\N{\fs90}- Well, maybe it is black and white. - And blurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.51,0:02:44.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,可能就是模糊的\N{\fs90}Maybe it's blurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.11,0:02:46.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,这让我纠结了一星期 所以我决定\N{\fs90}This has been driving me mad all week, so I decided
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:49.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,去苏格兰兜兜风 说实话\N{\fs90}to go for a drive on some of Scotland's, let's be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:51.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,公路超棒\N{\fs90}brilliant driving roads.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.55,0:02:54.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,它们太美妙了\N{\fs90}They are...They are fantastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.46,0:02:59.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,说到这个 事实上\N{\fs90}And actually, speaking of which,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:02.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,有叫北部高地倡议的东西\N{\fs90}something called the North Highland Initiative,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.63,0:03:04.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,是查尔斯王子发起的\N{\fs90}set up by Prince Charles,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:06.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,由此几年前诞生了北海岸500号公路\N{\fs90}a few years ago it came up with the North Coast 500.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.77,0:03:11.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在 它是苏格兰版的美国66号公路 \N{\fs90}Now, this was going to be Scotland's answer to Route 66 in America.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:15.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,数百公里的绝世风景 令人惊叹\N{\fs90}Miles of amazing scenery. Incredible road.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.28,0:03:17.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里有张局部照片\N{\fs90}Got a picture of a bit of it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.14,0:03:18.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,看哪\N{\fs90}Look at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.35,0:03:19.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,大获成功\N{\fs90}Huge success.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.91,0:03:21.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,土豪们慕名而来\N{\fs90}Loads of big spenders came
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,开着他们的兰博基尼 法拉利和保时捷\N{\fs90}with their Lamborghinis, and their Ferraris and their Porsches.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.19,0:03:26.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,旅馆住满 饭店爆棚\N{\fs90}Hotels were full, restaurants were packed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:28.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,当地经济腾飞\N{\fs90}Local economy booming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.89,0:03:31.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以你觉得要过多久\N{\fs90}So how long do you think it was
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:32.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,当地的报纸的头条\N{\fs90}before the local newspaper
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.83,0:03:35.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,会包含以下两个词\N{\fs90}carried a headline containing the following words:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:37.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,"警方"和"镇压"\N{\fs90}"police" and "crackdown"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.00,0:03:40.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,十天\N{\fs90}Ten days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.13,0:03:41.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,-两天吧 -两天\N{\fs90}- Two days. - Two days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:44.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,"噢 我们不能让人在上面开车\N{\fs90}"Oh, we can't have people driving along that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:45.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,你很可能会撞到路人"\N{\fs90}You might run into a pedestrian!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.57,0:03:47.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是条路\N{\fs90}It's a road!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.54,0:03:50.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,我就知道 然后就有了A9公路\N{\fs90}I know it is. And then you've got the A9.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.11,0:03:58.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,160公里布满测速相机\N{\fs90}Ninety-nine miles of continuous average speed camera.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.35,0:04:00.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,-160吗？-160公里\N{\fs90}- Ninety-nine? - Ninety-nine miles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.82,0:04:03.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,不好意思各位 我猜你们都是车迷吧\N{\fs90}Now, I'm sorry, you lot, I presume you're all petrolheads, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.46,0:04:05.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs90}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:07.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,那我来问你们一个问题\N{\fs90}So let me ask you a question.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.00,0:04:10.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,在很多年后 \N{\fs90}Dying in your beds,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:11.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,你临终之际\N{\fs90}many years from now...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.57,0:04:16.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,你愿意用这所有\N{\fs90}...would you be willing to trade all the days,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:18.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,剩下的日子\N{\fs90}from this day to that,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.94,0:04:20.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,来换取一个机会\N{\fs90}for one chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.38,0:04:22.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,只有一次机会\N{\fs90}just one chance,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.98,0:04:27.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,回到这里 告诉苏格兰安全摄像头企业\N{\fs90}to come back and say to the Scottish Safety Camera Partnership,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:29.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,"你们可以拿走我们的驾照\N{\fs90}"You can take our licences,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:32.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,但你们夺不走我们的自由"\N{\fs90}but you can't take our freedom"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.69,0:04:36.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,自由 自由\N{\fs90}AUDIENCE: Freedom! Freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.76,0:04:39.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,自由 自由 自由\N{\fs90}Freedom! Freedom! Freedom! Freedom! Freedom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:41.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,看看你干了些什么\N{\fs90}Now look what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.17,0:04:45.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家\N{\fs90}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.57,0:04:47.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,看看你的所作所为\N{\fs90}Look what you've done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:48.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我知道 -这很危险\N{\fs90}- I know. - That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:50.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我知道 -让我们继续节目\N{\fs90}- I know. - Let's get on with the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:54.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 在今晚的汽车节目中\N{\fs90}Yes. In tonight's car programme...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:57.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,罐子里有只蚂蚁\N{\fs90}An ant in a jar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:00.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,一只狗在引路\N{\fs90}A dog on a lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.75,0:05:04.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,桌子上有些豆\N{\fs90}And some beans on a table.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:07.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是首先\N{\fs90}But first,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.69,0:05:08.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,当有人想买一辆\N{\fs90}when someone wants to buy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.92,0:05:10.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,又大又快的轿车\N{\fs90}a large and very fast saloon car,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.49,0:05:12.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们喜欢买德国车\N{\fs90}they tend to buy German.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:15.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们觉得没其他选择\N{\fs90}They think there is no alternative.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.60,0:05:17.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,但真的没有吗\N{\fs90}But is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.04,0:05:27.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是一辆雷克萨斯GS F\N{\fs90}This is the Lexus GS F.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:32.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,一眼就知道 这不是辆很好看的车\N{\fs90}And straight away, we can see that it isn't an especially handsome car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且这是辆雷克萨斯\N{\fs90}And it's a Lexus,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:37.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,表明车主是个高尔夫发烧友\N{\fs90}which marks its owner out as a golf enthusiast
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:40.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,或者是个呆子\N{\fs90}and possibly... a bore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:43.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,更糟的是\N{\fs90}And things are worse
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.59,0:05:47.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,当你试图和它共处的时候\N{\fs90}when you try to live with it for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.13,0:05:50.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,烦人的是 除了方向盘上的那些按钮\N{\fs90}The most annoying thing, apart from the buttons on the steering wheel,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.20,0:05:54.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,似乎所有按钮都会把收音机调到你不喜欢的电台\N{\fs90}all of which seem to retune the radio to a station you don't like very much,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.57,0:05:57.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,不光这个 每当你想伸手\N{\fs90}apart from that, every time you reach for
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.64,0:06:00.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,拿杯架上的提神饮料时\N{\fs90}a can of zesty drink in the cup holder...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:03.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,我又手贱了\N{\fs90}I've done it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.45,0:06:05.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,你总会不小心碰到鼠标\N{\fs90}You can't help but nudge the mouse
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:08.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,它会把导航的目的地设置到\N{\fs90}which sets the destination on the satnav
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:11.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,你现在的位置\N{\fs90}to where you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.09,0:06:13.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,在300米后 右转\N{\fs90}SATNAV: In 300 yards, right turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.49,0:06:16.16,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不用你告诉我怎么走\N{\fs90}I don't need to be told how to get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:17.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,我已经在这儿了\N{\fs90}I'm already here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.76,0:06:19.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,右转 然后右转\N{\fs90}Next right, then right turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:22.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢天哪 现在它想让我退回去\N{\fs90}Oh, God. Now it's trying to make me go back there a few yards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.96,0:06:24.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,我开过了啊\N{\fs90}I was there!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.10,0:06:29.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以 除了这个费事又讨厌的导航\N{\fs90}So, apart from a fiddly and annoying satnav...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,前方右转 然后右转\N{\fs90}SATNAV: Next right, then right turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.91,0:06:35.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,这7万英镑还能买到什么\N{\fs90}...what else do you get for your ￡70,000?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.21,0:06:40.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,额 讲真没什么了\N{\fs90}Er... Not much, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:42.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,车里没有Wi-Fi\N{\fs90}Er... You don't get Wi-Fi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.48,0:06:44.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,没有苹果Carplay 或者手势控制\N{\fs90}or Apple CarPlay, or gesture control.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.02,0:06:48.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,连双离合变速箱都没有\N{\fs90}You don't even get a DSG gearbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:51.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,行驶时座椅不能按摩\N{\fs90}Seats don't massage you as you drive along,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:52.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,也不会自动泊车\N{\fs90}it can't park itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.70,0:06:56.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,但有一个DVD播放器\N{\fs90}But you do get a DVD player.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.36,0:06:58.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,这多怀旧啊\N{\fs90}And how 1996 is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.33,0:07:04.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,这辆车配置匮乏 还烦人\N{\fs90}This car, then, is sparsely equipped and annoying.
