Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.68,0:07:19.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,首先 是它的引擎\N{\fs90}First of all, there's the engine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.19,0:07:23.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,宝马和奔驰都使用涡轮增压\N{\fs90}BMW and Mercedes both use turbocharging
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:24.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,来达到动力需求\N{\fs90}to balance the need for power
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.89,0:07:27.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,和排放要求的平衡\N{\fs90}with the need for good emissions...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.33,0:07:29.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,但这辆车不是\N{\fs90}but this doesn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.60,0:07:32.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,它把燃料和空气混合\N{\fs90}This mixes the fuel with the air,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.63,0:07:35.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后 没耍什么花招\N{\fs90}and then, with no trickery at all,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.24,0:07:36.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,就这么点燃了\N{\fs90}blows it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.41,0:07:44.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,当然 这意味着\N{\fs90}Of course, that does mean
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:46.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,GS F对动物们不太友好\N{\fs90}the GS F isn't very kind to animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:49.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,但毫无疑问 这是件坏事\N{\fs90}And that's a bad thing, make no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:53.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,但从好的方面看\N{\fs90}But on the upside,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:56.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,听听它发出的噪音\N{\fs90}listen to the noise it makes!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:03.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,中转速时 它听起来很凶恶\N{\fs90}At medium revs, it sounds baleful,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.57,0:08:06.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,就像一条孤单的狗\N{\fs90}like a... lonely dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.90,0:08:11.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,但当你拉高转速时 它就像它自己\N{\fs90}But when you build the revs up, it sounds like what it is:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.81,0:08:15.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,一台5升的自然吸气V8\N{\fs90}a normally aspirated five-litre V8.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:24.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,它发出的功率和扭矩\N{\fs90}It doesn't produce anything like the power or the torque
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,比不上德国的竞争对手\N{\fs90}you get from its turbocharged German rivals,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:28.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,但就纯粹的激情而言\N{\fs90}but for sheer excitement...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.79,0:08:35.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,就像被女神挠痒了一样\N{\fs90}It's like being tickled by a goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.70,0:08:42.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且它也不是很慢\N{\fs90}And it's not exactly slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.74,0:08:53.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,它百公里加速4.5秒\N{\fs90}It does 0-60 in four-and-a-half seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:58.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,最高时速能达到272公里\N{\fs90}And flat out, it'll do nearly 170 miles an hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:02.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后是操控性\N{\fs90}And then there's the handling.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.33,0:09:09.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,很难相信这是一辆\N{\fs90}It's hard to believe that this is a large
