Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:15.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,后备箱大到能放下高尔夫球杆\N{\fs90}with a boot that's big enough for your golf bats
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.20,0:09:18.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,和所有的共济会用品\N{\fs90}and all your Freemasonry paraphernalia,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.41,0:09:21.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为 它感觉像一辆跑车\N{\fs90}because... it feels like a sports car.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.28,0:09:27.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,你可以用各种开关和按钮\N{\fs90}You can change the way the car behaves
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.82,0:09:30.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,来调整车辆的表现\N{\fs90}with various knobs here and buttons here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.95,0:09:32.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,但我把所有东西都关了\N{\fs90}but I've got everything turned off
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.05,0:09:36.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以我能体验一下没有电子辅助\N{\fs90}so I can get a feel for how the car behaves
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.26,0:09:40.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,这辆车会如何表现\N{\fs90}without an electronic safety blanket.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.46,0:09:41.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且我很喜欢\N{\fs90}And I like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.12,0:10:03.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,看看这个\N{\fs90}Look at that.
