Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.86,0:10:09.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,这太棒了\N{\fs90}it's fantastic!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fs90}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:15.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,是时候再来杯提神饮料了\N{\fs90}Time for another zesty drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.83,0:10:17.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢 我去\N{\fs90}Oh, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:20.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,-三百米后...  -我知道我在哪儿\N{\fs90}- SATNAV: In 300 yards... - I know where I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:22.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,前方右转 然后右转\N{\fs90}Next right. Then right turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:26.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢 饶了我吧\N{\fs90}Oh, for God's sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:28.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果是日常生活用车\N{\fs90}For living with on a day-to-day basis,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.84,0:10:31.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,德国车要好得多\N{\fs90}German cars are far better.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.31,0:10:36.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,但作为一台驾驶机器 你会对这结论感到惊讶\N{\fs90}But as a driving machine, and you may find this conclusion surprising...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.35,0:10:39.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,我认为GS F吊打它们\N{\fs90}I think the GS F has them licked.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.50,0:10:51.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧\N{\fs90}Well, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.80,0:10:57.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在\N{\fs90}Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:11:02.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,我要说 今年晚些时候新的宝马M5要发布了\N{\fs90}Now, I should point out, there is a new BMW M5 coming later this year,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:04.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,但它要超过GS F可不容易\N{\fs90}but it'll have to go some to be better than that GS F.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.95,0:11:06.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,-的确 -是的\N{\fs90}- It really will. - Yeah, yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.78,0:11:09.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,但在制作的时候有多少动物受到了伤害\N{\fs90}But exactly how many animals were harmed in the making of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.75,0:11:12.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,-很多动物 -还有一只是乌龟\N{\fs90}- A lot! - One of them was a tortoise!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.42,0:11:14.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,我知道 我们先无视吧\N{\fs90}I know. Let's gloss over that, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.66,0:11:18.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们来看看它在埃博拉症赛道上能跑多快\N{\fs90}And let's find out now how fast the Lexus goes round the Eboladrome.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.96,0:11:21.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,当然 这就要把它交给那个人\N{\fs90}And that, of course, means handing it over to a man
