Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.34,0:11:32.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,他蓄势待发\N{\fs90}He's coiled and ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.64,0:11:34.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,他出发了\N{\fs90}And he's off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:38.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,释放出所有471匹马力\N{\fs90}Unleashing all the 471 wailing horsepower
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:41.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,开始不直道上的第一次冲刺\N{\fs90}for the first sprint of the Isn't Straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.12,0:11:43.92,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里面都是什么破烂玩意儿\N{\fs90}What the hell does all this shit do in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:46.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,他需要的只是两个踏板和一个方向盘\N{\fs90}All he needs is two pedals and a wheel
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:49.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,就能霸气外露\N{\fs90}to unleash the full shock and awe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.52,0:11:51.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,牵引力控制系统\N{\fs90}Traction control?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.33,0:11:54.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果你想要有自己思想的东西\N{\fs90}If you want something with a mind of its own...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.50,0:11:56.70,字幕,,0,0,0,,买匹马 找个老婆\N{\fs90}get a horse, get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:12:00.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,幸运的是 他不需要电子辅助\N{\fs90}Fortunately, he doesn't need the electronic nannies.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:02.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,全力进入留你名弯\N{\fs90}Pushing it hard up to Your Name Here,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.40,0:12:05.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在全靠这强大的布伦博卡钳\N{\fs90}and now leaning on the mighty Brembo brakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.97,0:12:09.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里轻一点 让扭矩矢量差速器发挥作用\N{\fs90}Gentle now, letting the torque-vectoring diff do its thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.01,0:12:11.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,再次踩下油门\N{\fs90}And then back on the throttle
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:15.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,强大的V8得以再次一展歌喉\N{\fs90}so that mighty V8 can sing its song once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.85,0:12:18.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果他们让我带枪的话\N{\fs90}If they would have let me bring my gun,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.09,0:12:20.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,我现在可能已经自杀了\N{\fs90}I'd have probably shot myself by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.22,0:12:23.06,字幕,,0,0,0,,那实在是浪费人才\N{\fs90}And that would be a waste of great talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.12,0:12:26.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 再次快速通过不直道\N{\fs90}Right, another fast dash up the Isn't,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:30.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,八速自动变速箱快速降档\N{\fs90}and now shifting rapidly down the eight-speed automatic
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.40,0:12:32.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,到达老奶房弯\N{\fs90}as he arrives at Old Lady's House.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.63,0:12:36.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,精准给油通过颠簸的赛道\N{\fs90}Feeding it precisely through there on this damp track,
