Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:46.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,还剩两个弯\N{\fs90}Two corners left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.58,0:12:48.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里走线很紧\N{\fs90}Tidy through there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.25,0:12:50.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,只剩绵羊坡弯了\N{\fs90}Just Field of Sheep to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.63,0:12:54.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,抓地力到极限了 冲过终点\N{\fs90}And he's right on the edge of the grip and across the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.10,0:12:59.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,看起来的确不错\N{\fs90}It did look good. It did look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.51,0:13:01.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,-的确不错 -成绩怎么样\N{\fs90}- It did look good. - How did it do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.48,0:13:03.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,啊哈\N{\fs90}A-ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:06.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 来看看在圈速榜上表现如何\N{\fs90}Well, now let's find out where it goes on the Lap Board.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.51,0:13:08.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,别忘了 这是湿地圈\N{\fs90}Remember, it was damp.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.72,0:13:12.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢 哇哦\N{\fs90}Oh, wow! Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.35,0:13:15.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,这比旧款的宝马还要慢\N{\fs90}So it's slower than an already-out-of-date BMW,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:17.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,它让你像个共济会员\N{\fs90}it makes you look like a Freemason,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.52,0:13:19.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,它还会让动物爆炸\N{\fs90}and it causes animals to explode.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.59,0:13:21.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 但是\N{\fs90}Yes. Yes, but--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.86,0:13:23.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 但你又给了一个优秀的推荐 杰里米\N{\fs90}Yes, but it's just another of your excellent recommendations, Jeremy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:25.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,非常感谢 没有关系\N{\fs90}Thank you very much. Never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:27.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 真是谢谢你了\N{\fs90}Yes, thank you very much, indeed.
