Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.61,0:14:10.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,奔驰没有意识到\N{\fs90}The thing Mercedes haven't realised is that we,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.41,0:14:12.11,字幕,,0,0,0,,我相信你肯定同意\N{\fs90}and I'm sure you all agree with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.18,0:14:14.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们和车之间形成了感情纽带\N{\fs90}we form an emotional bond with our car.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.55,0:14:15.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我们心系爱车 -正是\N{\fs90}- We're attached to them. - Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.78,0:14:17.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以把车租给别人\N{\fs90}So renting it to someone else
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.18,0:14:18.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,就像把你的宠物租给别人\N{\fs90}would be like renting out your pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:20.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 或者你的丁丁\N{\fs90}Yeah, or your penis.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:25.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是的 -我心系着它 就是这个意思\N{\fs90}- Yes. - I'm attached to it, I mean. That's what I mean.
