Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.13,0:14:35.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是我想说的 奔驰显然没好好动脑子\N{\fs90}And that's what I'm on about. Mercedes has obviously got it into its head,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.94,0:14:38.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,这实在让我担忧 因为奔驰是大企业\N{\fs90}and this really worries me, because it's a large car company,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:42.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果车只是工具 就像微波炉 或者冰箱一样\N{\fs90}that cars are just tools, like microwave ovens or fridge freezers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:45.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,那我们就很乐意 "借呗 反正我不在乎"\N{\fs90}that we'll just sort of gladly, "Borrow it. I don't really care."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:47.38,字幕,,0,0,0,,你太对了 它们都有感情的\N{\fs90}You're absolutely right. They are very emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:50.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为如果你有辆车 最后卖掉了\N{\fs90}Because you know if you have a car, eventually you sell it,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.28,0:14:53.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,但当你看见别人开它的时候 总会难过\N{\fs90}but then you see somebody else driving around in it, that always feels bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:57.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,就像你看见前女友和别人嘿嘿嘿一样\N{\fs90}It's a bit like watching your ex-girlfriend do sex with someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.86,0:15:03.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,对的 在衣柜里熬了一晚上以后 深有体会\N{\fs90}No. And after a terrible evening in a wardrobe, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:06.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,奇怪地深蚀人心\N{\fs90}It's strangely undermining.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.97,0:15:11.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,不好意思打断一下 看到湖里的圆圈了吗\N{\fs90}I'm sorry to interrupt. See those circles in the lake just there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.67,0:15:14.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,-水怪 水怪啊\N{\fs90}- Monster! Monster! It's a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:18.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我刚刚看见... 有人看见了吗 -是水怪 水怪\N{\fs90}- I just saw... Did anyone else see that? - Monster! Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:20.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,早说了 是真的\N{\fs90}It's real. I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.78,0:15:23.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们没法统一意见 湖里有水怪吗\N{\fs90}Since we can't agree on this, is there a monster in the loch?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:25.49,字幕,,0,0,0,,有\N{\fs90}AUDIENCE: Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.55,0:15:28.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 他们住这儿 肯定知道\N{\fs90}Right, there you go. They live here, they would know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.39,0:15:32.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果没水怪 那这里的旅游业怎么搞\N{\fs90}And if there were no monster, what would you do for a tourist industry up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:35.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,卖没有水怪图案的抹布\N{\fs90}Sell tea towels without monsters on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.00,0:15:37.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 我不买账 因为你说的是\N{\fs90}No, I'm not having that, because what you're saying is,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:40.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,"来美丽的苏格兰吧" 就像你说的 路美风景美\N{\fs90}"Come to beautiful Scotland." As you've said, lovely roads, lovely scenery.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:42.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,这儿有个酒店 有个美丽的湖\N{\fs90}There's a hotel, a beautiful lake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.57,0:15:44.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们为什么要说 "是啊 但这有个水怪"\N{\fs90}Why would they say, "Yeah, but there's a monster"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.77,0:15:46.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,就好像在说 "来约克郡吧\N{\fs90}That would be like saying, "Come to Yorkshire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.64,0:15:49.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,它很美丽 你知道我们这儿有瘟疫吗"\N{\fs90}It's beautiful. We've got the plague, you know?"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.31,0:15:51.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,-肯定不会这么说 -我们有点分心了\N{\fs90}- They they wouldn't do that. - We've got distracted a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:54.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,-有点跑题 -我们在说什么来着\N{\fs90}- We have got a bit off-topic. - What were we talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.35,0:15:57.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们在说他躲在衣柜里\N{\fs90}We were talking about him hiding in a wardrobe,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:15:58.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,看他的前女友嘿嘿嘿\N{\fs90}watching an ex-girlfriend have sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.79,0:16:01.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,-是的 说漏了 -是有点说漏了\N{\fs90}- Yeah, that was an over-share. - It was a bit of an over-share.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.82,0:16:04.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,要不就是他把丁丁租出去的事 我忘了\N{\fs90}It was either that or he'd rented his penis out. I can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:06.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,类似这些事\N{\fs90}Something along those lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.43,0:16:08.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,但实际上 我们想和车建立情感纽带\N{\fs90}But actually, there's a point I just want to make on this
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.03,0:16:11.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,是有原因的\N{\fs90}about this emotional connection we have with our cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:14.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,你知道报废一辆车是什么感觉吗 非常悲惨\N{\fs90}Cos you know when you scrap a car? It really is very tragic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.57,0:16:17.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,你目送着与你经历风雨的车进入粉碎机\N{\fs90}When you watch a car that's got all those shared memories going into the crusher.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.74,0:16:19.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,-穷途末路了 -是的\N{\fs90}- It's the end of the road. - It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.44,0:16:21.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,有个新的组织\N{\fs90}There's this... a new organisation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:24.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,叫做慈善汽车 你可以把车给他们\N{\fs90}It's called Charity Car, where you can give your car to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.35,0:16:27.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,他们搞定所有的手续 然后拿走你的车\N{\fs90}they deal with all the paperwork and what have you and take your car away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:31.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后他们把募集的钱捐给你指定的慈善组织\N{\fs90}Yeah? And then they give the money that they raised to a charity of your choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.69,0:16:34.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,-好主意 我喜欢 -好点子\N{\fs90}- That's a nice idea. I like that. - It is a nice idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.26,0:16:36.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,这样一来 虽然车没了很难过\N{\fs90}So that, you know, it's sad your old car's gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.62,0:16:40.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是有一头驴子能被拯救\N{\fs90}but now... you know, a donkey can be rescued.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:43.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,你的车就能在野驴的微笑中永远活着\N{\fs90}And your car lives on in the smile of an abandoned donkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.07,0:16:46.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,太感人了 这就是我们要做的\N{\fs90}That's a beautiful thing. That's what we're about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.90,0:16:49.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是节目的精髓 走心\N{\fs90}That's what this show is, it's all heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.07,0:16:53.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,-就是我们 -爱心和道路安全:\N{\fs90}- It's what we are. - Heart and road safety: those are the two pillars
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.91,0:16:56.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,支撑我们节目的两大支柱\N{\fs90}that underpin everything, really, on this show.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我要跟你唠嗑一下 -是吗\N{\fs90}- I've got some conversation for you. - Have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:17:01.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 有这么一个网站\N{\fs90}Yes, which is that there's a website that tells you
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.12,0:17:02.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,它会告诉你在英国的公路上\N{\fs90}how many of any given type of car
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:06.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,还剩下多少种型号的汽车\N{\fs90}are still left on the roads of Britain today, yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:08.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,恐怕有一些坏消息\N{\fs90}And I'm afraid we have some sad news.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:10.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 实在是忧心\N{\fs90}Yeah, we do. This is a big worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:13.33,字幕,,0,0,0,,你还记得雪铁龙Saxo VTS吗 就是它\N{\fs90}You remember the Citroën Saxo VTS, yeah? There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.39,0:17:15.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,愤怒小混混之车\N{\fs90}The car of the angry yob.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.30,0:17:18.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,很适合飞身下车再偷把电锯进去\N{\fs90}It is the ideal car to nip out and steal a chainsaw in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.47,0:17:21.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,一辆绝妙的 像样的 刺激的小掀背 我很喜欢\N{\fs90}A fabulous, proper, fizzy little hatchback. Loved it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.57,0:17:24.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,在2008年 还有5000辆这车\N{\fs90}Well, in 2008, there were 5,000 of them on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:28.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,-今年 只剩491辆了 -看到没\N{\fs90}- This year, 491 left on the road. - See?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.24,0:17:30.34,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且事实上 这令人担忧\N{\fs90}And, in fact... I know, this is a worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.41,0:17:32.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,看 这有个图表 我们画的\N{\fs90}Look, we've got a little chart. We've drawn this up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:36.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,按这个速度 到2019年 它就灭绝了\N{\fs90}At that rate, by 2019, they'll all have gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:39.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有沃克斯豪尔Calibra 16V\N{\fs90}There's also the Vauxhall Calibra 16V.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:41.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,这里有张照片 我们过去很爱它\N{\fs90}There's a picture. We used to love that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.42,0:17:45.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,你知道吗 这款车只剩323辆了\N{\fs90}Do you know, there are only 323 of those left,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.86,0:17:48.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,一年之内就会灭绝\N{\fs90}and they could be extinct within a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:51.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,有趣的是 全世界的人都在努力\N{\fs90}And what's interesting is there are people all over the world
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.97,0:17:56.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,保护老虎不至灭绝\N{\fs90}working hard to save the tiger from extinction,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.54,0:17:58.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,然而却没有人\N{\fs90}but nobody is doing anything
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.14,0:18:00.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,保护Calibra 16V\N{\fs90}to save the Vauxhall Calibra 16V.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.61,0:18:02.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,-我们似乎发现了些什么 -不并没有\N{\fs90}- We've identified something here. - No, there isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:06.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,然而 还是有好消息的 莫瑞斯Ital\N{\fs90}However, there is some good news in all of this. The Morris Ital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.15,0:18:09.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,一共有175000...\N{\fs90}175,000 of these...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.85,0:18:12.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,...坨这样的屎\N{\fs90}turds were made,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.32,0:18:14.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,被奥斯汀汽车拉出来\N{\fs90}were squeezed out by the Austin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:20.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,在2015年 它只剩35辆了\N{\fs90}And in 2015, there were only 35 left.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.53,0:18:23.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 现在欢呼吧\N{\fs90}Yes! Now you can cheer!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:26.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,-这是好消息 -的确\N{\fs90}- That is good news. - It's good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:28.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,路上只有35辆\N{\fs90}Only 35 on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:32.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 等等等等 你说得很对\N{\fs90}No. Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait, wait, wait. You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:37.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,别急着庆祝 是的 2015年只剩35辆\N{\fs90}But before you celebrate, yes, 35 left on the road in 2015.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.54,0:18:41.45,字幕,,0,0,0,,-嗯哼 -在2016年 有47辆\N{\fs90}- Mm-hm. - In 2016... there were 47.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.52,0:18:43.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,什么 居然还能增长\N{\fs90}What, so they're going up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.38,0:18:46.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,-它们在繁衍吗 -不\N{\fs90}- Are they mating? - No. No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:48.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,我认为是有人在复原它\N{\fs90}I think people are restoring them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.19,0:18:50.26,字幕,,0,0,0,,-什么人 -疯子\N{\fs90}- What people? - Mad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:52.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,-无论如何 有可能你是对的 但我做了一个计算\N{\fs90}Anyway, look... No, you're possibly right, but I've done a calculation.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.96,0:18:56.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,这速率是 一年内增长了34%\N{\fs90}And at that rate... That's a 34% increase in just one year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.36,0:18:59.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,按这个速度 到2044年\N{\fs90}And at that rate, by the year 2044,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.60,0:19:05.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,所有175000辆Ital都会回到路上\N{\fs90}all 175,000 Morris Itals will be back on the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.21,0:19:06.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,-噢我的天 -简直是灾难\N{\fs90}- Oh, my God! - This is a disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.91,0:19:09.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 女士们先生们 这就是英国脱欧\N{\fs90}It is. That, ladies and gentlemen, is Brexit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.41,0:19:14.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是他们想要的: 英国倒退\N{\fs90}That's what they want: backwards with Britain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.42,0:19:18.22,字幕,,0,0,0,,是时候了 因为唠嗑街已经走到底\N{\fs90}It is time now, since we've reached the end of Conversation Street,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.25,0:19:20.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们挂入倒挡 来看看这个\N{\fs90}to select reverse and have a look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.22,0:19:22.76,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是宾利Bentayga\N{\fs90}This is the Bentley Bentayga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.82,0:19:26.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,巨型奢华四驱的\N{\fs90}A massive, luxurious, four-wheel-drive
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:28.66,字幕,,0,0,0,,SUV猎装车\N{\fs90}SUV shooting brake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.73,0:19:30.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,问题是\N{\fs90}The question is,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.26,0:19:33.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是辆好车 还是只是一坨...\N{\fs90}is it any good, or is it a load of...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.13,0:19:35.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,一坨啥呢\N{\fs90}What's the word?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:45.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,为了找到答案 詹姆斯把它带到了\N{\fs90}Well, to find out, James brought it here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.48,0:19:47.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,德国的阿尔卑斯山\N{\fs90}to the German Alps.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.15,0:19:52.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 我直接说明白\N{\fs90}Right, I'll get straight to the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.25,0:19:55.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,它太棒了\N{\fs90}It is tremendous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:58.46,字幕,,0,0,0,,对于这车有件重要的事要记住\N{\fs90}The important thing to remember about this car is this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.53,0:20:02.20,字幕,,0,0,0,,它不是辆越野车 也不是SUV\N{\fs90}It's not an off-roader, it's not an SUV.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.26,0:20:05.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,最重要的是 它是辆宾利\N{\fs90}First and foremost, it's a Bentley.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.37,0:20:06.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是这辆车的灵魂\N{\fs90}That's what this car is about.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.03,0:20:10.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,我已经爱上它了\N{\fs90}I'm already loving it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:14.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,然而 你猜怎么着\N{\fs90}But then... guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.88,0:20:17.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,问题在于 这辆宾利裸车\N{\fs90}The problem is that a barebones Bentley
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:21.18,字幕,,0,0,0,,价格为16万英镑\N{\fs90}costs ￡160,000,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.25,0:20:24.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,而少花12000英镑\N{\fs90}and for ￡12,000 less than that,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.35,0:20:25.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,你却可以得到这个\N{\fs90}you can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.02,0:20:31.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,一辆能唱能跳 配置齐全\N{\fs90}An all-singing, all-dancing, everything-fitted-as-standard
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.06,0:20:34.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,5升机械增压的路虎揽胜\N{\fs90}5L supercharged Range Rover.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:40.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,或者再少花12万英镑 你可以得到这个\N{\fs90}Or, for ￡120,000 less than that, you can have this,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.10,0:20:41.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,新款捷豹F-PACE\N{\fs90}the new Jaguar F-PACE.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.61,0:20:47.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,这可不是花园棚屋\N{\fs90}And it's not like this thing is a garden shed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.67,0:20:49.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,它配备了各种智能部件\N{\fs90}It's got loads of clever stuff on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.48,0:20:51.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,如果你从超市回来\N{\fs90}So if you're coming back from the shops
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:52.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,手里抱着沉重的袋子\N{\fs90}with your arms full of heavy bags,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.91,0:20:55.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,你可以用脚打开后备箱\N{\fs90}you can open the boot with your foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.38,0:20:59.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,-揽胜也有这功能 -是 但它贵了12万英镑\N{\fs90}- Yeah, but I can do that with a Range Rover. - Yes, but it's ￡120,000 more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.42,0:21:02.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,-而且你还没有这个 看 -那是啥\N{\fs90}- And you don't get one of these. Look. - What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:05.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是个防水的便携手环\N{\fs90}It's a waterproof, go-anywhere bracelet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.59,0:21:08.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,你可以用它锁车\N{\fs90}that you use to lock...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.46,0:21:09.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,解锁车 还能发动引擎\N{\fs90}and unlock it, and start the engine,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.86,0:21:12.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以你不用随身带钥匙了\N{\fs90}so you don't need to carry keys in your pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:14.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,这...\N{\fs90}That...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.57,0:21:17.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,-这还真是个好点子 -是啊 很机智\N{\fs90}- That's actually quite a good idea. - I know, it's brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.44,0:21:20.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,-你怎么给它充电 -不知道 可能就像手表一样\N{\fs90}- How do you charge it up? - I don't know. Maybe it's like one of those watches.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.44,0:21:24.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,-噢 看哪 -噢\N{\fs90}-Oh, hello. - Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:26.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,吹牛老爹来了 \N{\fs90}Puff Daddy is arriving.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.11,0:21:28.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,你觉得他戴大金链子了吗\N{\fs90}Do you think he's wearing a chain?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.78,0:21:31.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,那玩意儿是捷豹的四倍价钱\N{\fs90}You know, that thing costs four times more than the Jag.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:34.09,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且不像徽章那样差异明显\N{\fs90}And it's not like the badges are that different.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.15,0:21:37.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,捷豹是一辆车\N{\fs90}That Jag is... a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.66,0:21:39.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,这更像是一种声明\N{\fs90}This is more of a statement.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.86,0:21:41.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是对生而为人的\N{\fs90}This is a new way of understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.56,0:21:42.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,新式诠释\N{\fs90}the condition of being human.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:44.47,字幕,,0,0,0,,奢华的最终证明\N{\fs90}It is the last word in luxury.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:46.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,这个证明还真是贵\N{\fs90}It's a very expensive statement, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.50,0:21:49.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,买这玩意的钱 能买那台捷豹\N{\fs90}I mean, if you've got the money to buy that, you could buy the Jag
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.84,0:21:53.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,还剩130,000磅 能雇个公关经理\N{\fs90}and still have ￡130,000 to spend on a PR agent
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.11,0:21:55.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,上晨间访谈节目吹嘘自己了\N{\fs90}to put you on breakfast TV talking about how great you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.84,0:21:57.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,它贵130,000磅是有原因的\N{\fs90}It costs ￡130,000 more for a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.98,0:22:00.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,捷豹车主都是爱幻想的中年男人\N{\fs90}Jags are for deluded middle-aged men
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.21,0:22:02.75,字幕,,0,0,0,,整天沉浸在种马的幻想中\N{\fs90}who entertain tragic fantasies about being Lotharios.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.82,0:22:04.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,我懂 我有四辆\N{\fs90}I know, I've had four of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:07.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,-要说喜欢幻想的品牌 -嘿\N{\fs90}-If you're talking about brands with delusion - hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.45,0:22:09.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,-首选的就是宾利  -两位\N{\fs90}-Bentley, that's what it is. -Guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:12.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,-怎么  -在停车场可不能分辨高下\N{\fs90}-What? -We are not gonna sort this out in a car park.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.39,0:22:14.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们得去试驾\N{\fs90}We need to go for a drive,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.90,0:22:18.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,我在地图上已经确定好路线了\N{\fs90}and I have worked out a route on this map here, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.67,0:22:21.87,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们在紫薇村\N{\fs90}We are in the village of... Wank,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.94,0:22:26.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,从紫薇村出发 到亲亲乡\N{\fs90}and we'll go from... Wank to Kissing,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.41,0:22:28.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,再到摸摸寨\N{\fs90}then on to Petting.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.44,0:22:30.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后... 到这\N{\fs90}Then... this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.65,0:22:33.48,字幕,,0,0,0,,最后到领证村\N{\fs90}And then... Wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.55,0:22:36.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以是紫薇 亲亲 摸摸 (哔~) 领证\N{\fs90}So, Wank, Kissing, Petting, (BLEEP), Wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.95,0:22:42.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,没错 在中欧可以走遍人生旅途\N{\fs90}Yes. It'll be a journey through life without leaving Central Europe.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.76,0:22:44.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,是的 出发吧\N{\fs90}Yeah, it will. Let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.79,0:22:46.59,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们十分性奋\N{\fs90}Very excited,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.66,0:22:51.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,踏上了德国人所谓的浪漫之旅\N{\fs90}we set off on what the Germans call the Romantic Road.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.94,0:22:57.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们离开了紫薇村\N{\fs90}So, we are leaving the town of Wank.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.04,0:23:00.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,那是什么 "谢谢..."\N{\fs90}What's that? "Thank you for..."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.31,0:23:01.94,字幕,,0,0,0,,什么 哦好的\N{\fs90}What? Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.45,0:23:08.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,只过了几分钟\N{\fs90}And after just a few minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.62,0:23:11.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,就发生了很不寻常的事情\N{\fs90}something very unusual happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.25,0:23:14.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,伙计们\N{\fs90}Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.76,0:23:16.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,我想不出话说\N{\fs90}I can't think of anything to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.56,0:23:19.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,松了一口气\N{\fs90}What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.46,0:23:21.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 我是真的想不出\N{\fs90}No, but I really can't,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.09,0:23:25.27,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为如果你想要一辆大型豪华越野车\N{\fs90}because if you want a large, luxury off-roader,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.33,0:23:26.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,你就买揽胜\N{\fs90}you buy a Range Rover.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.87,0:23:28.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,结束\N{\fs90}The end.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.10,0:23:30.04,字幕,,0,0,0,,结案 继续\N{\fs90}The end, move on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:33.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,然而詹姆斯\N{\fs90}James, however,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.87,0:23:37.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,对他的Bentayga有很多话要说\N{\fs90}had lots to say about his Bentayga.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.61,0:23:38.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,嘿老兄 你知道吗\N{\fs90}Hey, chaps, did you know
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.01,0:23:42.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,我车上有18个扬声器\N{\fs90}the stereo in my car has got 18 speakers?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.72,0:23:45.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,才这么点 我有27个\N{\fs90}Is that all? Mine's got 27.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.69,0:23:47.52,字幕,,0,0,0,,嗯 都在放垃圾歌\N{\fs90}Yeah, all playing rubbish.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.59,0:23:50.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,谢谢 哈蒙德\N{\fs90}Thanks, Hammond.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.69,0:23:52.79,字幕,,0,0,0,,其实27个扬声器不是重点\N{\fs90}Actually, 27 speakers is not the point.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.86,0:23:57.73,字幕,,0,0,0,,它的音响有1950瓦功率\N{\fs90}My car stereo produces 1,950W,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.80,0:24:01.57,字幕,,0,0,0,,它是车载音响功率最大的车\N{\fs90}making it the most powerful stereo ever put in a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.64,0:24:06.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,实际上 音响是车内唯一能响的东西了\N{\fs90}In fact, it's about the only thing in here that does make a noise.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.81,0:24:10.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,这有点像在大英图书馆里开车\N{\fs90}This is a little bit like driving along in the British Library.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.04,0:24:13.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,非常安静 非常优雅\N{\fs90}It's very quiet, it's very refined.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.78,0:24:16.78,字幕,,0,0,0,,地毯非常厚\N{\fs90}The carpets are very thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.85,0:24:19.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,这意味着 当你踩下踏板的时候\N{\fs90}Which means you simply aren't ready for what happens
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.42,0:24:21.56,字幕,,0,0,0,,你不知道会发生什么\N{\fs90}when you put your foot down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.76,0:24:32.07,字幕,,0,0,0,,它配备了全新的600马力W12引擎\N{\fs90}So this has an all-new W12 600-horsepower engine,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.13,0:24:35.90,字幕,,0,0,0,,就像身处于皮革包裹的火山爆发中\N{\fs90}and it's like being in a leather-trimmed volcanic eruption.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.14,0:24:39.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,它不加速 而是直接爆炸\N{\fs90}It doesn't accelerate, it goes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.18,0:24:45.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的姑奶奶\N{\fs90}Bloody Nora!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.38,0:24:50.72,字幕,,0,0,0,,可惜的是 杰里米想出要说的了\N{\fs90}Sadly, at this point, Jeremy thought of something to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.78,0:24:52.55,字幕,,0,0,0,,看到了吗 那是希特勒\N{\fs90}See that? That's the prison
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.55,0:24:55.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,写下《我的奋斗》的监狱\N{\fs90}where Hitler wrote Mein Kampf.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.76,0:24:59.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,嗯 你想说什么呢\N{\fs90}Yeah. Where are you going with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.76,0:25:04.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,没什么\N{\fs90}Nowhere, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.57,0:25:07.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,只是觉得你们会想知道\N{\fs90}Just thought you might like to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.17,0:25:10.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 我们回到车上\N{\fs90}Good. Let's get back to the cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.47,0:25:13.67,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为现在捷豹和路虎是一家公司的\N{\fs90}Now, you might be thinking that because Jaguar is owned by the same company
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.74,0:25:18.71,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以你会觉得这是辆贴捷豹牌的神行者\N{\fs90}that own Land Rover, this is just a Freelander with a Jaguar badge on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.78,0:25:20.05,字幕,,0,0,0,,但并不是\N{\fs90}but it's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.38,0:25:23.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,车身下是和捷豹XE相同的\N{\fs90}Underneath is the same basic aluminium structure
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.95,0:25:26.02,字幕,,0,0,0,,全铝车架\N{\fs90}you find under a Jaguar XE,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.09,0:25:29.86,字幕,,0,0,0,,XE是好车 所以这很好\N{\fs90}which is a fantastic car, so that's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.92,0:25:32.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,我的确只有3升的机械增压V6\N{\fs90}I do only get a 3L supercharged V6,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.69,0:25:35.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,也就是375马力\N{\fs90}which means 375 brake horsepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.86,0:25:40.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,比船长那辆少了225马力 讲真\N{\fs90}That's 225 less than James's, let's be honest,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.23,0:25:41.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,那就是辆真皮的Q7\N{\fs90}leather-lined Audi Q7.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.84,0:25:44.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,但是这辆车很轻\N{\fs90}But this is light,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.67,0:25:46.74,字幕,,0,0,0,,所以没那么笨拙\N{\fs90}so it ain't no slouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.38,0:25:51.31,字幕,,0,0,0,,我喜欢它的操控\N{\fs90}I like the way this thing handles itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.38,0:25:53.61,字幕,,0,0,0,,我喜欢它转向的方式\N{\fs90}I like the way, when you change direction,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.68,0:25:55.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,它控制了车重\N{\fs90}when you turn, it controls its weight,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.75,0:25:57.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,过弯时重心转移\N{\fs90}what there is of it, across the axles.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.92,0:26:01.25,字幕,,0,0,0,,让人觉得敏捷又有活力\N{\fs90}That makes it feel nimble, eager.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.32,0:26:05.29,字幕,,0,0,0,,不会有坐在豪宅里掉下悬崖的感觉\N{\fs90}It doesn't feel like I'm sitting in a stately home falling off a cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.76,0:26:11.63,字幕,,0,0,0,,不久 我追上了船长\N{\fs90}Soon, James was in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.33,0:26:15.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢看呐\N{\fs90}Oh, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.20,0:26:18.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,你应该来我这儿 这儿能看见白金汉宫\N{\fs90}James, you should be where I am. You can see Buckingham Palace and...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.07,0:26:20.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,哦不 是你的车屁股\N{\fs90}Oh, no, it's the back of your car.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.47,0:26:24.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,我喜欢有人跟在后面 你是要去度假吗\N{\fs90}I like it when my man is following me. Do you have the luggage for the weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.41,0:26:29.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,得了吧 詹姆斯\N{\fs90}Come on, James.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.65,0:26:33.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,可能你的马力用不完 但你挡路了\N{\fs90}You might have all the horsepower in the world, but you are in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.02,0:26:38.93,字幕,,0,0,0,,省省吧 伯明翰小子\N{\fs90}Stay with that, Birmingham boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.23,0:26:51.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,詹姆斯 你是怕开太快了家具会晃吗\N{\fs90}James, are you worried all your furniture will slide about if you go any faster?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.44,0:26:58.08,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢隧道\N{\fs90}Oh, tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.14,0:27:00.41,字幕,,0,0,0,,很好 我有正事要做\N{\fs90}Excellent. I have important work to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.02,0:27:12.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,贱民们真是干什么都要发出点声音\N{\fs90}Honestly, the plebs make such a noise about everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.76,0:27:14.96,字幕,,0,0,0,,这就是"运动多功能车"里的"运动"\N{\fs90}That is putting the S back in SUV.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.03,0:27:18.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,这是辆很运动的SUV\N{\fs90}This is a sporty sports-utility vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.17,0:27:22.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,这项运动还不是钓鱼\N{\fs90}And the sport is not fishing.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.47,0:27:25.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,可惜 娱乐时间被大猩猩\N{\fs90}Sadly, our playtime was then interrupted
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.91,0:27:28.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,恼人的电话打断了\N{\fs90}by a worrying call from Clarkson.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.27,0:27:32.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,伙计们 我收到制片人的短信\N{\fs90}Erm... guys, we've had a text from Mr Wilman.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.95,0:27:35.62,字幕,,0,0,0,,噢天呐 他说什么\N{\fs90}Oh, God. What does it say?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.72,0:27:39.15,字幕,,0,0,0,,他说为了区分性能的差异\N{\fs90}It said that to sort out the performance differences,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.22,0:27:41.35,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们要去附近的一个机场\N{\fs90}we should go to a nearby airstrip,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.42,0:27:44.12,字幕,,0,0,0,,他准备了一场竞速\N{\fs90}where he'd laid on some competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.59,0:27:46.89,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们去了\N{\fs90}So we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.37,0:27:57.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,伙计们 这是我们的竞争对手\N{\fs90}Chaps, this is what we're up against.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:57.50,0:28:00.54,字幕,,0,0,0,,宝马X5 M\N{\fs90}BMW X5 M.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.61,0:28:04.01,字幕,,0,0,0,,4.4升双涡轮增压 567马力\N{\fs90}4.4L, twin-turbocharged, 567 horsepower.
