Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.66,0:28:24.77,字幕,,0,0,0,,这辈子都赢不了\N{\fs90}Not in a million years.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.27,0:28:34.81,字幕,,0,0,0,,抱歉浪费你们的时间来比赛了\N{\fs90}Sorry about wasting your time with this race.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.78,0:28:39.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,你可以发布一辆车 时速一百万英里\N{\fs90}You could launch a car that does a million miles an hour
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.01,0:28:41.98,字幕,,0,0,0,,只卖8毛钱 还能在水上开\N{\fs90}and costs 8 pence and runs on water,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.05,0:28:44.58,字幕,,0,0,0,,但人们还是会买揽胜\N{\fs90}and people would still buy Range Rovers,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.65,0:28:47.99,字幕,,0,0,0,,因为不然买啥呢\N{\fs90}because why would you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.05,0:28:50.82,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 空调关闭\N{\fs90}OK, air-conditioning is off.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.89,0:28:55.36,字幕,,0,0,0,,现在是动态模式 变速箱在运动模式\N{\fs90}It's in dynamic mode, gearbox is in sport.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.43,0:28:57.50,字幕,,0,0,0,,给力啊 小捷豹\N{\fs90}Come on, little Jag.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.56,0:29:00.43,字幕,,0,0,0,,我并不担心粉红小猪的威胁 \N{\fs90}So I'm not really worried about Pinky and Perky's challenge,
