Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.18,0:29:13.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,就在他们决定明年的狩猎季\N{\fs90}before they choose what colour Range Rover they'd like
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.98,0:29:16.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,要买什么颜色的揽胜之前\N{\fs90}for next year's shooting season.
