Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.80,0:30:10.30,字幕,,0,0,0,,好的 做得好 詹姆斯\N{\fs90}Yes, yes. Well done, James.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.37,0:30:13.17,字幕,,0,0,0,,谁会想到 如果花四倍的钱买车\N{\fs90}Oh, who knew, if you spend four times as much on a car,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.24,0:30:15.51,字幕,,0,0,0,,就会比另一辆车稍微快一点点呢\N{\fs90}you get one that's a tiny bit faster than another?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.58,0:30:18.91,字幕,,0,0,0,,嘘 你们还没明白吗\N{\fs90}Ssh! You two just haven't got the message, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:18.98,0:30:22.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,-明白什么 你输了吗 -好吧...\N{\fs90}- What, that you lost? - Yeah. Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.35,0:30:24.95,字幕,,0,0,0,,不 这很明白了 就像内裤\N{\fs90}No, the message is very clear. Underpants, OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.02,0:30:27.69,字幕,,0,0,0,,你可以在商场货架上买条便宜的\N{\fs90}You can buy a cheap pair from a market stall,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.75,0:30:31.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,或者可以买一条含有金丝的昂贵内裤\N{\fs90}or you can buy an expensive pair with gold thread in them,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.46,0:30:35.10,字幕,,0,0,0,,或者像其他人一样 去玛莎百货买\N{\fs90}or you can do what everyone does, you go to Marks & Spencer's.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.16,0:30:37.23,字幕,,0,0,0,,玛莎百货 如果你不是英国人\N{\fs90}Marks & Spencer's, if you're watching this not in the UK,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.30,0:30:39.53,字幕,,0,0,0,,那就是所有人买内裤的地方\N{\fs90}is where we all buy our pants from.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:39.60,0:30:41.00,字幕,,0,0,0,,但我不去那儿买\N{\fs90}Well, I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.34,0:30:47.14,字幕,,0,0,0,,比赛过后 我们继续旅途\N{\fs90}After the race, we resumed our journey,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.21,0:30:51.24,字幕,,0,0,0,,而理查德和詹姆斯则继续斗嘴\N{\fs90}and Richard and James resumed their bickering.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.31,0:30:55.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,F-PACE是啥意思 听起来像家用清洁剂\N{\fs90}What does F-PACE mean? It sounds like a domestic cleaning product.
