Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.83,0:31:45.97,字幕,,0,0,0,,由于杰里米提到了钱的问题\N{\fs90}Since Jeremy had brought up the subject of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.97,0:31:50.84,字幕,,0,0,0,,我不知道他们是如何做到34000磅起卖\N{\fs90}I don't know how they can sell you one of these for from 34 grand.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.97,0:31:52.44,字幕,,0,0,0,,而且这辆 包含所有选配的\N{\fs90}And this one, with everything on it,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.51,0:31:55.28,字幕,,0,0,0,,除了V6机械增压引擎\N{\fs90}quite apart from a V6 supercharged engine,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.34,0:31:57.88,字幕,,0,0,0,,还有真皮内饰 iPhone接口\N{\fs90}it's got leather everything, iPhone connectivity,
