Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.98,0:32:07.32,字幕,,0,0,0,,所有这些只要51000磅 怎么做到的\N{\fs90}All of that still only costs 51 grand. How do they do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.39,0:32:12.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,和别的一比 这就是世纪大钜惠啊\N{\fs90}Next to everything else, it suddenly looks like the bargain of the century.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.19,0:32:15.03,字幕,,0,0,0,,杰里米 这辆车比你的车好\N{\fs90}Jeremy, this car is better than yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.10,0:32:18.83,字幕,,0,0,0,,好吧 它并不是 对吗\N{\fs90}Well, now, it just isn't, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.90,0:32:21.37,字幕,,0,0,0,,你就是个... 什么词来着\N{\fs90}You're being a... What's the word?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.41,0:32:31.21,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们飞速穿过亲亲乡\N{\fs90}We then flashed through the village of Kissing,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:31.28,0:32:33.65,字幕,,0,0,0,,越快完事儿越好\N{\fs90}getting it over with as quickly as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.48,0:32:37.68,字幕,,0,0,0,,然后经过摸摸寨\N{\fs90}Then we went through Petting.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.75,0:32:40.85,字幕,,0,0,0,,为了保证在睡觉前\N{\fs90}And to make sure we reached erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.92,0:32:43.19,字幕,,0,0,0,,能够上三垒\N{\fs90}third base before bedtime,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.26,0:32:46.39,字幕,,0,0,0,,我们决定打开导航\N{\fs90}we decided to set our satnavs.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.46,0:32:49.80,字幕,,0,0,0,,请说出国家名\N{\fs90}SATNAV: Please name the country.
