Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.27,0:33:29.60,字幕,,0,0,0,,我没法说 人们听着呢\N{\fs90}I can't say it. People are listening.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.67,0:33:32.64,字幕,,0,0,0,,没有听清\N{\fs90}SATNAV: Sorry?
