Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.93,0:33:57.40,字幕,,0,0,0,,不久 我们穿过边境进入奥地利\N{\fs90}And soon, we crossed the border into Austria.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.46,0:34:00.13,字幕,,0,0,0,,奥地利非常非常美丽\N{\fs90}It's very, very pretty, Austria.
